{assign var="active" value="logistic"}

<div class="row login">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="shopyheader">
                <h2>{l s='Functionalities for physical stores and warehouses' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 shopyinfopanel">
                <h2>{l s='Functionalities for physical stores and warehouses' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question1" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question1">
                        {l s='Logistics' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse in" id="question1">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Our system unifies all the tools you need to keep efficient control of your logistics operations. You will be able to create multiple warehouses, manage your physical stores, take inventories from tablets, control stock in real time, carry out audits, and much more..." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question2" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question2">
                        {l s='Can a product be located throughout the logistics system?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question2">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Yes, at any time, from any point of sale or from any administration terminal it is possible to know the location and the number of units available of a product in all warehouses or physical stores, including its location within the warehouse." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question3" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question3">
                        {l s='Can the products be ordered within the warehouse?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question3">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Yes, Shopylinker's warehouse and point of sale management allows you to define shelves, levels and drawers in which products are placed or stored." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question4" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question4">
                        {l s='Does the logistics system include stock control and order optimization?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question4">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="The logistics system is responsible for making all the calculations to optimize stock and orders. It analyzes the delivery times of the suppliers and also takes into account the number of daily sales of each product. These values can be calculated automatically from history or manually by entering data by the manager." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question5" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question5">
                        {l s='How orders are placed?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question5">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="In our logistics system, each warehouse and physical store has its own configured suppliers. Employees with access to each warehouse have the option of placing their orders with the available suppliers. You can place a general order with several suppliers and our system will take care of sending individual orders to each of them. This improves the order process, optimizing it." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question6" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question6">
                        {l s='How are orders received in the different warehouses?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question6">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Once the order is placed, authorized collaborators will have the option of receiving it in whole or in part. If the warehouse has the racking structure already established, they will be able to place the products on them at the time of receiving the order." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question7" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question7">
                        {l s='What inventory management methods can be applied to warehouse management?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question7">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="Each of the warehouses created in the logistics system can have the stock removal method configured independently, either as LIFO (Last In First Out) or FIFO (First In First Out)." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/logistics/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-_630OciGo"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Create a warehouse' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W2q4QcMOZMk"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Definition of the warehouse structure' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question8" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question8">
                        {l s='Point of sale (POS)' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question8">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="System that will allow you to connect your physical stores with your PrestaShop in an easy and effective way. It includes features such as scanner billing, price verification, and catalog billing. In addition, it will allow you to keep a detailed record of sales, have an inventory in real time and perform cash audits." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/point-of-sale/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqw1k7jf3SI"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Creation of physical store'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
            {include file="module:shopylinkerp/views/templates/admin/sidebar.tpl" var=active}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
